name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.qjournal.finalize-segment.timeout.ms
description:
Quorum timeout in milliseconds during finalizing for a specific
    segment.

name: dfs.client.socketcache.capacity
description:
Socket cache capacity (in entries) for short-circuit reads.
    If this value is set to 0, the client socket cache is disabled.

name: fs.s3a.paging.maximum
description:
How many keys to request from S3 when doing
     directory listings at a time.

name: dfs.client.read.shortcircuit.buffer.size
description: Buffer size in bytes for short-circuit local reads.
